ErrorMessage: Stores the message strings for Support Error Codes.
There's "/DatabaseInfo" at FS root, then the rest is stored at "/{first 4 error digits}/{last 4 error digits}/".
BrowserDll: Mounted as "shareddata:/". Contains various browser data: emojis, OSS NROs, "buildinfo/buildinfo.dat", ...

Help: HTML resources: Open-source licenses
("Intellectual Property Notices") and seizure warnings("Health & Safety Information").
The former is stored at FS "/legallines.htdocs/"
while the latter is at "/safe.htdocs/".
Dictionary: European, English, and Japanese dictionaries.
AvatarImage: Background and Character images for user avatars (RGBA format & Yaz0 compression).
LocalNews: Tutorial images and strings. Used for the offline news by the News applet.
CertStoreCruiser (BrowserCertStore): Currently not present on retail devices.
FontBfcpx: Currently not present on retail devices.
SystemUpdate: Contains the title-listing for the associated sysupdate in the NCA-type0 .cnmt.
BootImagePackage: Firmware Package A: Normal Firmware.
BootImagePackageSafe: Firmware Package B: SafeMode Firmware. See Boot_Modes#Safe_Mode: Safe Mode.
BootImagePackageExFat: Firmware Package C: Normal Firmware (exFAT variant). Identical to 0100000000000819 with different FS sysmodule. Requires a device ID to download from CDN.
BootImagePackageExFatSafe: Firmware Package D: SafeMode Firmware (exFAT variant). Identical to 010000000000081A with different FS sysmodule. Requires a device ID to download from CDN.
ControllerIcon: Controller gfx/icon data + dummy file.
ControllerFirmware: Firmware binaries for peripherals (hardware within Joy-Cons/etc).
NgWord2: Contains version.dat and ac_*_nx files. All of the *_nx files stored under here are compressed with gzip.
ApplicationBlackList: Used by NS_Services: NS for restricting application installation and updates.
RebootlessSystemUpdateVersion: Rebootless system update version file.
FunctionBlackList: Used for restricting specific features in applications.
PlatformConfigCalcio: Calcio system config. Currently not present on retail devices.
NgWordT: Bad words for China region (Tencent).

New ErrorMessage: [16.0.0+] Currently not present on NX retail devices. Used by nn::err::detail::MountErrorMessageSystemData when the input nn::err::ErrorMessageDatabaseType is non-zero (retail NX Error_Applet: LibraryAppletError passes hard-coded value 0).
qlaunch (SystemAppletMenu): qlaunch system applet. Launched by NS_Services#LaunchSystemApplet: ns.
overlayDisp (OverlayApplet): ProgramId is loaded by NS_Services: ns from system-config-title.
set (LibraryAppletSet): Not present on retail devices.
PlayReport: Not present on retail devices.
maintenance (MaintenanceMenu): Initial applet displayed when booting into Recovery_Mode: recovery mode. Launched by NS_Services#LaunchSystemApplet: ns.
NS_Services: ns when a certain flag is non-zero, in multiple places including around code using the string "application_install".
NS_Services: ns when saving a SystemPlayReport with EventId "systemupdate_dl_throughput".
NS_Services: ns when saving a SystemPlayReport with EventId "volume_update" or "output_target_update".
gift (LibraryAppletGift): Not present on retail devices.

userMigration (LibraryAppletUserMigration): Not present on retail devices.
